ygData.messageBody:
I sure haven't.. but then again I never expected
it to be on time. I life in the Netherlands and when
I ordered EQ last year it took UPS 2 friggen months
to get it here! And that was with their 50 dollar 7
days worldwide program! And they want me to pay extra
because I wasn't home when the UPS guy showed up! Needles
to say i won't pay them and they can take me to
court if they want to... Anyhow just wondering about
who the lucky ones are... here's the recent poll from
EQvaullt (at the moment I entered)<br><br>Players
Poll:<br>Will you be traveling to Kunark tomorrow?<br>Idon't
even have Kunark!;56.1%<br>Yes! Rabid Sand Giants
couldn't keep me away!;25.7%<br>No, it will be way too
crowded. I'll wait a bit.;18.1%
